r />\n遊行期間舉牌支持比較好<br />\n一黎我地應該先做好自己<br />\n 無野比香港成功光復更鼓勵<br />\n二黎遊行期間舉牌比較曖昧<br />\n 比人既訊息係支持但又spin唔走你個訴求"},{"pid":"29db19a8928e208aa318262993007a0c04f955fd","tid":1669810,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:44:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d322cbc4ea2401609d7be3ba4d509863bfdbe08d","tid":1669810,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"icon so cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b094fa575e475ff20fe373b55b73d243f88125","tid":1669810,"uid":117509,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"搞手同參加既人其實意願唔太重要<br />\n支持自由同抗暴，聲援加泰相信冇人反對<br />\n但重要係，的確係一個好機會比土共抹黑都搞獨立<br />\n加上藍精靈同陳同佳輸左兩仗<br />\n我唔認為佢地會放棄咁好機會轉移視線"},{"pid":"29fdf8891253ba1c04a8c6c1c6fad90c9a03bdf1","tid":1669810,"uid":193032,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔好搞啦取消啦，好明顯百害而無一利"},{"pid":"799f913166862cfdc795817ef18adf38d748a203","tid":1669810,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:49:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d34a47bfd1c398d03f10418365809d40e0fdb7d9","tid":1669810,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d52e472366448507850a56d9004a0ff6f41440b","tid":1669810,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd373a79da69a910a148ee45a048c4d65fc8649f","tid":1669810,"uid":284304,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:40:01.000Z","msg":"根本呢種集會就好容易比人spin到支持獨立<br />\nsolomon咁講已經係提曬水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:50:15.000Z","msg":"最容易係講埋其他國家<br />\n提埋印尼"},{"pid":"225b3bbe306a8356e2f3726361a8f8ab036186d2","tid":1669810,"uid":17381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:50:39.000Z","msg":"時機未到 希望真手足諗多步 4個月唔易捱<br />\n係長期作戰冇得急 能夠表達到追求民主反政權暴力當然好 但一旦扣上支持加獨 俾媒體抺黑加中共d文宣機器可以即時